parameters: Tch... Who the hell are you guys...
Just a little longer, let's buy some time.
Phew, it seems like we managed somehow.

Masamune-kun, you've grown too. I couldn't have
won alone.
I want to be able to support Amelia quickly.
I can't do it without Masamune-kun anymore.

I guess it ended easily because we were dealing
with students after all.

That's right. I do have a feeling that I wanted to
stay as a student a little longer.
The school uniform suits you well...
Really...? I thought it might be tough at my age.
We can still keep going. You're incredibly cute.
